You are the only one that can save it and bring back the light into this world.
Are you prepared to go against the torrent of will, mortal?

▼ Gods from all realms are ready to bless you.
Gods of Olympus, Asgard, and Osiris await your arrival.
They will stand beside you, aid you, and fight with you on the battlefield.

Humans, Orcs, Beasts, Demons, and the Undead are rallying their forces for you.

Mortal, chosen one of the Absolute, bring honor to your Gods!
Someone is waiting for you atop the highest blood-stained point.

▼ The Gods will determine if you are worthy of their challenge.
They will test you to see if you are worthy to enter the Hall of the Gods.
Overcome their obstacles with wisdom and grace!
